3.5.name: wordpress/jcarousel-horizonal-slider
3.5.description:
jCarousel is a jQuery plugin for controlling a list of items in horizontal or vertical order. The items, which can be static HTML content or loaded with (or without) AJAX, can be scrolled back and forth (with or without animation).

This is a very good page gallery jcarousel Slider. when you add you gallery page looks very awesome .

Features:

  • No coding required!
  • Smart gallery jcarousel Slider. Build dynamic jcarousel slideshows from blog content

Requirements: PHP5+, WordPress 2.8.6+

Important Links: Demo
